issue.title: feat: Thai handwriting font
issue.body:
### Description:
This pull request addresses the issue of missing font support for Thai Unicode characters in Excalidraw by introducing a fallback font named ~~SanamDeklen~~ Itim.

### Proposed Changes:
In this pull request, we propose adding a fallback font named ~~SanamDeklen~~ Itim to address the missing font support for Thai Unicode characters. This font is well-suited for Thai script and will enhance the readability and aesthetics of Thai text within Excalidraw.

### What I did:
- [x] The ~~SanamDeklen~~ Itim font files have been added to the project.
- [x] The font fallback mechanism has been updated to include ~~SanamDeklen~~ Itim for Thai Unicode characters.
